title: TransTeleCom
extract: TransTelecom (Russian: ТрансТелеКо́m (ТТК)) is a major telecommunications company in Russia that owns one of the largest networks in the world of fiber optical cables.
extract_html: TransTelecom (Russian: ТрансТелеКо́m (ТТК)) is a major telecommunications company in Russia that owns one of the largest networks in the world of fiber optical cables.
